   914→      );
   915→
   916→      // Strip [TTS]...[/TTS] block from the text message after audio is sent.
   917→      // This fires after sendQueue completes, so the draft message already exists.
   918→      // stripPattern is best-effort and handles missing/finalized drafts gracefully.
   919→      if (attachment.type === "audio") {
